blueprint.label: Quad-Rail Junction (restricted turns)
blueprint.description:
42.0 TPM (with penalty stations)
39.3 TPM (without penalty stations)

Reduced turning crossing.
- No U-turns (necessary with trains longer than 11).
- Penalized left turns.

Remove the "X" stations to allow left turns freely or add duplicate stations beside them for an even higher penalty.

Track can be removed to prevent left turns from outside lanes or right turns from inside lanes.
